short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Puts health score badges onto delivery service websites for San Francisco restaurants.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension puts health scores and health inspection info from the San Francisco Department of Public Health directly onto the food ordering pages of popular delivery websites. Easily order food online from the vendor of your choice, while remaining more informed about the health and safety standards of the restaurants you are ordering from.

The extension currently supports the following delivery services:
-Caviar
-Postmates.
More services coming soon!

The extension currently supports San Francisco restaurants only.
